{"tid":2056208,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到完場] 我的土著鄰居","createTime":"2020-06-08T13:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T16:25:20.000Z","uid":35070,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3c205fe30649b999a5ea92da00396fd18080b32c","tid":2056208,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:35:10.000Z","msg":"在《我的土著鄰居》這套破格的紀錄片中，Moffatt一家獲邀遷到納米比亞居住一個月，每位家庭成員都有好獨特的體驗。面對當地族人的提問和評價，這個家庭不得不重新審視一直以來固有的生活方式，反思自己的價值觀；各種習以為常的觀念，如身體形象與審美眼光、貧富差距、社交媒體、性和忠誠、消費與浪費、以至男性和女性的角色，在辛巴族人的眼光下，碰撞出一段段苦樂參半的互動和對話，讓雙方經歷人生中寶貴的一課。"},{"pid":"3db8a0f29c95dd51e9f0df7577ec4a8cdc4e8d1c","tid":2056208,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"#1: 初來報到<br />\nMoffatt一家來到納米比亞的辛巴族人部落，見到村中心聳立一幢平房，由外到內均仿照著他們英國居所去興建，十分驚訝。情況就像打開隨意門，英國與納米比亞只是一門之隔！"},{"pid":"69edbc08bffe60f791a61afde2e71b4c5cacf8eb","tid":2056208,"uid":228801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c54d76648c4e4239baaa8eaf657376105bb7e6f","tid":2056208,"uid":48604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"題材幾新穎"},{"pid":"581c67c45d860efa9eaf93776f4594ba5a851bd6","tid":2056208,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"[url][港台電視]我的土著鄰居  逢星期一晚 2130-2230<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2055275[/url]\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2055275[/url]